> [!NOTE] Пометка
> Декомпозиция go роудмапы из roadmap.sh/golang. Выписал основыне темы, на котороые стоит обратить внимание

### Основные темы

1. Basics
	- Type casting
	- Type Inference
	- Arrays, Slice, Maps
	- Make()
	- Structs
	- Errors, Panic, Recove
2. Deeper
	- Types, Type Assertion, Switches
	- Interfaces
	- Context
	- Goroutines
	- Channels
	- Buffer
	- Select
	- Mutex
	- Go Runtime
	- Generics
	- Working with JSON (Marshalling & Unmarshalling)
3. Web Frameworks
	- Gin
	- Echo
	- Gorilla
4. Logging
	- Log, Slog
	- Zerolog
	- Zap
5. API Clients
	- REST - Grequests
	- GraphQL - graphql-go
6. Testing Apps
	- Unit Testing
	- Mock Testing
7. Tools for Microservice
	- ProtoBuff
	- Grpc-go
	- Grpc-Gateway
	- Go-Kit
	- Watermill
